reviewText: The interview format in this movie is relatively boring compared to Vegitales usual format. My 2 yr old still likes it though.
My kids love it and it teaches good biblical values. Ages 2-11
Love veggie tales so much and this was the cutest version of the beloved Abraham and Sarah story of faith.
My students could (finally) connect a movie to the person we learned about!  What a fantastic Veggietales!  I can't wait to order more!
